{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-230-fibonacci-words","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 230: Reči Fibonaccija","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Za bilo koju sekvencu slova, $A$ i $B$, definišemo $F_{A,B}$ kao niz ($A, B, AB, BAB, ABBAB, \\ldots$) gde je svaki element kombinacija dva prethodna elementa.</p>\n<p>Nadalje, definišemo $D_{A,B}(n)$ kao $n$-ti broj u prvom elementu od $F_{A,B}$, koji uključuje najmanje broj $n$.</p>\n<p>Primer:</p>\n<p>Razmotrimo $A = 1\\,415\\,926\\,535$, $B = 8\\,979\\,323\\,846$. Želimo da nađemo $D_{A,B}(35)$, na primer.</p>\n<p>Prvi elementi za $F_{A,B}$ su:</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{align}\n&#x26; 1\\,415\\,926\\,535 \\\\\n&#x26; 8\\,979\\,323\\,846 \\\\\n&#x26; 14\\,159\\,265\\,358\\,979\\,323\\,846 \\\\\n&#x26; 897\\,932\\,384\\,614\\,159\\,265\\,358\\,979\\,323\\,846 \\\\\n&#x26; 14\\,159\\,265\\,358\\,979\\,323\\,846\\,897\\,932\\,384\\,614\\,15\\color{red}{9}\\,265\\,358\\,979\\,323\\,846\n\\end{align}$$</p>\n<p>Broj $D_{A,B}(35)$ je broj ${35}^{\\text{th}}$ u petom članu, koji je 9.</p>\n<p>Sada koristimo za $A$ prvih 100 cifara $\\pi$ iza decimalne tačke:</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{align}\n&#x26; 14\\,159\\,265\\,358\\,979\\,323\\,846\\,264\\,338\\,327\\,950\\,288\\,419\\,716\\,939\\,937\\,510 \\\\\n&#x26; 58\\,209\\,749\\,445\\,923\\,078\\,164\\,062\\,862\\,089\\,986\\,280\\,348\\,253\\,421\\,170\\,679\n\\end{align}$$</p>\n<p>i za $B$, sljedeћи broj koji je stotice:</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{align}\n&#x26; 82\\,148\\,086\\,513\\,282\\,306\\,647\\,093\\,844\\,609\\,550\\,582\\,231\\,725\\,359\\,408\\,128 \\\\\n&#x26; 48\\,111\\,745\\,028\\,410\\,270\\,193\\,852\\,110\\,555\\,964\\,462\\,294\\,895\\,493\\,038\\,196\n\\end{align}$$</p>\n<p>Pronađi $\\sum_{n = 0, 1, \\ldots, 17} {10}^n × D_{A,B}((127 + 19n) × 7^n)$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4531000cf542c50ff65","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301874,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-230-fibonacci-words"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function fibonacciWords() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nfibonacciWords();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>fibonacciWords()</code> should return <code>850481152593119200</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(fibonacciWords(), 850481152593119200);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-201-to-300","dashedName":"problem-230-fibonacci-words","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-231-the-prime-factorisation-of-binomial-coefficients","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-229-four-representations-using-squares","id":"5900f4531000cf542c50ff65","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-230-fibonacci-words"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}